          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Quite a few CCCA members also belong to the organization’s chartered Region where they live. Each year, Regional Events like region tours and grand classics allow members to interact with one another and have some fun. The regions cover the entire continental United States plus portions of Canada.",
