            "text": "Since CCCA began over half a century ago, the organization has faithfully engaged in outreach efforts. Car shows, The Classic Car magazine, plus CARavans events have allowed people who might not own a classic to interact with the community. There’s also the Classic Car Club of America’s Museum at the famous Gilmore Car Museum, which has been in existence since 1987.",
